  "texts": [
    "For the sake of this work, we focus only on single-inhabitant scenarios.",
    "The interaction of the user with the home environment leads to the generation of high-level events.",
    "For instance, when a magnetic sensor on the fridge fires the value 1, this implies that the subject opened the fridge.",
    "Let E = {𝑒 1, 𝑒 2,..., 𝑒 𝑛 } be the set of possible high-level events captured by the sensors.",
    "The continuous stream of such events is partitioned into fixed-time temporal windows (e.g., using overlapping sliding windows)."
  ],
